{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Phm|1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","chapter":1,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":1,"text":"Paul, a prisoner of Christ Jesus, and Timothy our brother:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":2,"text":"to Apphia our sister, to Archippus our fellow soldier, and to the church that meets in your home.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":3,"text":"Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":4,"text":"I always thank my God when I mention you in my prayers,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":5,"text":"because I hear of your love for all the saints and the faith that you have in the Lord Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":6,"text":"I pray that your participation in the faith may become effective through knowing every good thing that is in us for the glory of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":7,"text":"For I have great joy and encouragement from your love, because the hearts of the saints have been refreshed through you, brother.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":8,"text":"For this reason, although I have great boldness in Christ to command you to do what is right,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":9,"text":"I appeal to you, instead, on the basis of love. I, Paul, as an elderly man and now also as a prisoner of Christ Jesus,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":10,"text":"appeal to you for my son, Onesimus. I became his father while I was in chains.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":11,"text":"Once he was useless to you, but now he is useful both to you and to me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":12,"text":"I am sending him back to you —I am sending my very own heart.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":13,"text":"I wanted to keep him with me, so that in my imprisonment for the gospel he might serve me in your place.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":14,"text":"But I didn’t want to do anything without your consent, so that your good deed might not be out of obligation, but of your own free will.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":15,"text":"For perhaps this is why he was separated from you for a brief time, so that you might get him back permanently,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":16,"text":"no longer as a slave, but more than a slave —as a dearly loved brother. He is especially so to me, but how much more to you, both in the flesh and in the Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":17,"text":"So if you consider me a partner, welcome him as you would me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":18,"text":"And if he has wronged you in any way, or owes you anything, charge that to my account.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":19,"text":"I, Paul, write this with my own hand: I will repay it —not to mention to you that you owe me even your very self.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":20,"text":"Yes, brother, may I benefit from you in the Lord; refresh my heart in Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":21,"text":"Since I am confident of your obedience, I am writing to you, knowing that you will do even more than I say.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":22,"text":"Meanwhile, also prepare a guest room for me, since I hope that through your prayers I will be restored to you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":23,"text":"Epaphras, my fellow prisoner in Christ Jesus, sends you greetings, and so do","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":24,"text":"Mark, Aristarchus, Demas, and Luke, my coworkers.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","bookOrder":56,"chapter":1,"verse":25,"text":"The grace of the Lord Jesus Christ be with your spirit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Phm","chapter":1,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,3,4,8,17,23,25],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Greeting"},{"beforeVerse":4,"text":"Philemon’s Love and Faith"},{"beforeVerse":8,"text":"An Appeal for Onesimus"},{"beforeVerse":23,"text":"Final Greetings"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Paul, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" a prisoner "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:3","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Christ Jesus, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:1","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Timothy "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:1","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":1,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" our brother:"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"Heb 13:3","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":3},{"label":"Rm 1:1","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 16:1","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":1},{"label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to Apphia our sister, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read our beloved"},{"kind":"text","text":" to Archippus "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:17","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" our fellow soldier, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:25","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and to the church that meets in your home. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 12:12","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:5","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":5,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 4:17","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":17},{"label":"Php 2:25","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":25},{"label":"Ac 12:12","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":12},{"label":"Rm 16:5","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read our beloved"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I always thank my God when I mention you in my prayers, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"because I hear of your love "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 6:5","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:37","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":37,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:6","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:22","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:23","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":23,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 3:6","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 5:8","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":8,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:14","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 4:20","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":20,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" for all the saints and the faith that you have in the Lord Jesus. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 6:5","book":"Deu","chapter":6,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 22:37","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":37},{"label":"Gl 5:6","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":6},{"label":"Gl 5:22","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":22},{"label":"Eph 6:23","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":23},{"label":"1Th 1:3","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"1Th 3:6","book":"1Th","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"1Th 5:8","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":8},{"label":"1Tm 1:14","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"1Jn 4:20","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I pray that your participation in the faith may become effective "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:6","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" through knowing every good thing "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 1:31","book":"Gen","chapter":1,"verse":31,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 18:18","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"3Jn 11","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" that is in us "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read in you"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the glory of Christ. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gl 5:6","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":6},{"label":"Gn 1:31","book":"Gen","chapter":1,"verse":31},{"label":"Gn 18:18","book":"Gen","chapter":18,"verse":18},{"label":"3Jn 11","book":"3Jn","chapter":1,"verse":11}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read in you"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I have great joy and encouragement from your love, because the hearts of the saints have been refreshed "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:19","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" through you, brother."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 12:19","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":19},{"label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For this reason, although I have great boldness in Christ to command you to do what is right, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I appeal to you, instead, on the basis of love. I, Paul, as an elderly man "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or an ambassador"},{"kind":"text","text":" and now also as a prisoner "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:3","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Christ Jesus, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"Heb 13:3","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or an ambassador"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"appeal to you for my son, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:11","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Onesimus. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"In Gk, Onesimus means “useful”"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:9","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" I became his father "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 4:15","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" while I was in chains. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 2:11","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"Col 4:9","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":9},{"label":"1Co 4:15","book":"1Co","chapter":4,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"In Gk, Onesimus means “useful”"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Once he was useless to you, but now he is useful both to you and to me. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am sending him back to you —I am sending my very own heart. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Other mss read him back. Receive him, my own heart."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Lit you —that is, my own heart"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Other mss read him back. Receive him, my own heart."},{"marker":4,"text":"Lit you —that is, my own heart"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I wanted to keep him with me, so that in my imprisonment for the gospel he might serve me in your place. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But I didn’t want to do anything without your consent, so that your good deed might not be out of obligation, but of your own free will. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For perhaps this is why he was separated from you for a brief time, so that you might get him back permanently, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"no longer as a slave, but more than a slave —as a dearly loved brother. He is especially so to me, but how much more to you, both in the flesh "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and in the Lord. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:19","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 11:8","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":8,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"1Co 16:19","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":19},{"label":"Rv 11:8","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So if you consider me a partner, welcome "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:1","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" him as you would me. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 14:1","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And if he has wronged you in any way, or owes you anything, charge that to my account. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:13","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 5:13","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I, Paul, write this with my own hand: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 16:21","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" I will repay it —not to mention to you that you owe me even your very self. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 16:21","book":"1Co","chapter":16,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yes, brother, may I benefit from you in the Lord; refresh my heart in Christ. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Since I am confident of your obedience, I am writing to you, knowing that you will do even more than I say. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Meanwhile, also prepare a guest room for me, since I hope that through your prayers I will be restored to you."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Epaphras, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:7","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:12","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" my fellow prisoner in Christ Jesus, sends you greetings, and so do "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 1:7","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":7},{"label":"Col 4:12","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Mark, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 12:12","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 12:25","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:37","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":37,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:39","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":39,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:10","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":10,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 4:11","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":11,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":13,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" Aristarchus, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:29","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":29,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" Demas, and Luke, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:14","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 4:10","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":10,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"text","text":" my coworkers."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 12:12","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":12},{"label":"Ac 12:25","book":"Act","chapter":12,"verse":25},{"label":"Ac 15:37","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":37},{"label":"Ac 15:39","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":39},{"label":"Col 4:10","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":10},{"label":"2Tm 4:11","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":11},{"label":"1Pt 5:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":13},{"label":"Ac 19:29","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":29},{"label":"Col 4:14","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"2Tm 4:10","book":"2Ti","chapter":4,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Phm:1:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The grace of the Lord "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read our Lord"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 3:18","book":"2Th","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 11:8","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Jesus Christ be with your spirit. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 51:12","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":12,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Th 3:18","book":"2Th","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"Rv 11:8","book":"Rev","chapter":11,"verse":8},{"label":"Ps 51:12","book":"Psa","chapter":51,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read our Lord"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099556577}